page_title: 'Quickstart: Generate images with the REST APIs for Azure OpenAI Service'
page_description: Learn how to generate images with Azure OpenAI Service by using the REST APIs and the endpoint and access keys for your Azure OpenAI resource.
chunk_content: OutputThe output from a successful image generation API call looks like the following example. The `url` field contains a URL where you can download the generated image. The URL stays active for 24 hours.#### DALL-E 3```json{     "created": 1698116662,     "data": [         {             "url": "<URL_to_generated_image>",            "revised_prompt": "<prompt_that_was_used>"         }    ]} ```#### DALL-E 2 (preview)```json{    "created": 1685130482,    "expires": 1685216887,    "id": "088e4742-89e8-4c38-9833-c294a47059a3",    "result":    {        "data":        [            {                "url": "<URL_to_generated_image>"            }        ]    },    "status": "succeeded"}```---The image generation APIs come with a content moderation filter. If the service recognizes your prompt as harmful content, it doesn't generate an image. For more information, see Content filtering. For examples of error responses, see the DALL-E how-to guide.The system returns an operation status of `Failed` and the `error.code` value in the message is set to `contentFilter`. Here's an example:#### DALL-E 3```json{    "created": 1698435368,    "error":    {        "code": "contentFilter",        "message": "Your task failed as a result of our safety system."    }}```#### DALL-E 2 (preview)```json{   "created": 1589478378,   "error": {       "code": "contentFilter",       "message": "Your task failed as a result of our safety system."   },   "id": "9484f239-9a05-41ba-997b-78252fec4b34",   "status": "failed"}```---It's also possible that the generated image itself is filtered. In this case, the error message is set to `Generated image was filtered as a result of our safety system.`. Here's an example:#### DALL-E 3```json{    "created": 1698435368,    "error":    {        "code": "contentFilter",        "message": "Generated image was filtered as a result of our safety system."    }}```#### DALL-E 2 (preview)```json{   "created": 1589478378,   "expires": 1589478399,   "id": "9484f239-9a05-41ba-997b-78252fec4b34",   "lastActionDateTime": 1589478378,   "data": [       {           "url": "<URL_TO_IMAGE>"       },       {           "error": {               "code": "contentFilter",               "message": "Generated image was filtered as a result of our safety system."           }       }   ],   "status": "succeeded"}```---
